description: A crunchy, sweet, spicy and cheesy taco dish.
name: Prawn & Mango Tacos Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 medium mango, peeled, de-seeded and sliced inyto bite size chunks.
2 medium avocado, peeled, de-seeded and mashed

recipeInstructions.text: In a bowl, combine the cooked prawns with all the ingredients apart from the avocado, cream and cheese.
Combine everything fully and allow to set for 20 minutes.
Pre-heat the oven to 180Â°C and prepare a baking tray by placing the 8 taco shells.
Heat up a non-stick pan to a medium heat and empty the prawn mixture into the pan and fry for 5 minutes while tossing.
Remove from the heat and evenly fill each of the taco shells and bake in the oven for 3 minutes.
Remove from the oven and top with cheese, sour cream and avocado before serving.
